</md></sn><sn><md>### Cyclotella {.text-center}

:::.row
:::.col-12 .col-md-6
![img](https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgxl32EIJZfAsvwRojL9FM-9KTvzg8Ucvou-Boi2sXsG7UUjq663jQsXlCDDSTpjDMrkL0ZvPsNjOrzH1_HWzfgnAJSY-ZFopmaExHZHBcQmiuA3gQFjDpLViXv75GcAsqi3T8JeAX5qWY/s400/ana.jpg)
