+++

* **Family:** Stephanodiscaceae
* **Group:** Diatoms (Bacillariophyceae)
* **Color:** Golden-brown
* **Size:** 5–100 µm
* **Habitat:** Lakes, rivers, reservoirs
* **Identification:** Circular disc-shaped diatom with radial markings.
</md></sn><sn><md>### Phacus {.text-center}

:::.row
:::.col-12 .col-md-6
![img](https://objects.liquidweb.services/images/202409/inat_66e23e39221700.51924045.jpg)
