:::
:::

+++ Structure
![img](https://ask.learncbse.in/uploads/db3785/original/1X/7d02d4f9ab2cf1d5b9330b978e522fbd05e425cc.png)
+++

* **Family:** Zygnemataceae
* **Group:** Green algae (Chlorophyceae)
* **Color:** Bright green
* **Size:** 10–100 µm wide filament
* **Habitat:** Freshwater ponds, streams
* **Identification:** Spiral chloroplasts inside cells.
</md></sn><sn><md>### Scytonema {.text-center}

:::.row
:::.col-12 .col-md-6
![img](https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSecXYDlgVdBv_TgXsP1LlD4tvTOifoiSz09O9m5m23GeZlcnGjFMozlyJj&amp;s=10)
